undefeated is a 2011 documentary film directed by daniel lindsay and t.j. martin . the film documents the struggles of a high school football team , the &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; tigers of memphis , as they attempt a winning season after years of losses . the team is turned around by coach bill courtney , who helps form a group of young men into an academic and athletic team . lindsay and martin served as co-directors , cinematographers , sound &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and editors , recording more than 500 hours of footage .